Job Description
We are looking for an experienced professional Content Writer who has the ability to think creatively and write unique content for our different Web/Social media project platform.Demonstrated previous experience with online content creation. Experience with online and social media advertising. He/She must be creative and professional.
Job Specification
The candidate must possess excellent English writing and verbal skills. Candidate will be responsible for creating content on a variety of subjects for USA and Pakistan based projects .A Levels / O levels back ground students will be preferred. Excellent written skills in English is ESSENTIAL and spoken is preferred.Learning attitude & Quick Grasping PowerGood typing speed
